{'Product Name' : 'Intel Core i3-13100 Desktop Processor 4 cores (4 P-cores + 0 E-cores)', 'Price' : '124.81', 'Power Consumption' : '60 W','text': 'Used it in a fresh build on MSI Mortar wifi and Thermalright assassin x. Temps 3x on idle and 5x on load. Has all needed performance and with integrated graphics is all needed. With Gigabyte Eagle RTX 3060 OC got Fortnite Epic run 130fps @1080p and ~90fps @1440p. Black Mesa ultra @1440p got 100-200fps. Single Con: Could be better priced around 130 though. I decided to have this configuration to have the possibilty to upgrade to 13600k sometime later if needed for Graphics render software.', 'rating': '5.0 out of 5 stars', 'date': 'Reviewed in the United States on March 26, 2023'},
