{'Product Name' : 'Intel Core i9-11900F Desktop Processor', 'Price' : '199.9', 'Power Consumption' : '65','text': "The F in the processor name, indicates it does NOT have integrated graphics. That means you have to have a separate video card in your computer or you will not have any video.In fact if you are using a separate video card, you WANT a processor with the F in the model name. The processor and the graphics will work much better this way. I have one in my 'QuadStation' computer and it works great.Read more", 'rating': '5.0 out of 5 stars', 'date': 'Reviewed in the United States on July 31, 2023'},
