{'Product Name' : 'Intel Core i7 (12th Gen) i7-12700 Dodeca-core (12 Core) 2.10 GHz Processor', 'Price' : '265.48', 'Power Consumption' : '65','text': "quite fast I think based on CPUZ score, but it looks like the stock fan is not enough it can get 85+c on cpuz stress test, idles around 40c +- 5c,  my case has 4 fans and my room is 22-24c. I had a hard time fitting the stock fan on the motherboard, the pins would not go in easily so I had to remove it a few times I'm wondering if that affected the thermal paste so I might add some more and try again.Read more", 'rating': '5.0 out of 5 stars', 'date': 'Reviewed in Canada on June 16, 2022'},
